mods.Name: Subaru BRZ Bodykit
mods.Creator: NeoS44
mods.Description: Adds new wings and hood options while changing the front bumper of the rb kit. also has a roof box. hood delete and bumper delete options are available as well

mods.Name: Modernized issetta
mods.Creator: NeoS44

mods.Name: Corvette C8
mods.Creator: NeoS44

mods.Name: M5 Bodykit
mods.Creator: NeoS44
mods.Description: adds new sideskirts, rear bumper and front splitter. also adds a roof wing (race bumper) 2 new spoilers, and roof bars
